Feature: Custom Tags Management
  As a user
  I want to add a tag to my notes
  In order to facilitate their search

  Scenario: Creating tag
    Given I create a note 
    When I want to create a new tag
    And I write the tag and I create it
    Then the tag is created and available

  Scenario: Associating an existing tag to my note
    Given I create a note
    When I associate a tag
    And I submit my note
    Then the note is indexed with this tag on my feed